hopobject.body: I have my own business viagra cialis combo packs Well those Republicans want to drill in your parks! One of their demands for the budget was to increase offshore oil drilling, and more drilling on federally protected lands. They want looser regulations around ash coal, a suspension of the EPA's regulation of carbon emissions, etc. So not only do they not care about people's health, they don't care about the earth's health either.
